  <brief_title>fMRI Based EEG Neurofeedback as a Method of Enhancing Emotional Resilience Among Soldiers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Longitudinal Study of the Effect of Neurofeedback Training on Soldiers Emotional Regulation Ability and Mental Resilience to Stress.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
